### Doc ResearchAPI with Bing Search API Test
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/plan_search \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "마이크로소프트의 office제품에 대해 설명해주세요"
    }
  ],
  "max_tokens": 2000,
  "temperature": 0.3,
  "stream": true,
  "query_rewrite": true,
  "search_engine": "bing_search_crawling",
  "locale": "en-US",
  "include_web_search": true,
  "include_mcp_server": false,
  "verbose": true
}' --no-buffer

